1760   4AC2 CD A2 00        call    CHPUT
1761   4AC5 3E 20           ld  a,' '
1762   4AC7 CD A2 00        call    CHPUT
1763   4ACA 18 07           jr  PHLINELR
1764   4ACC             PHLINESPC:
